con:call.name: Add PAN 12345678901234567
con:call.con:request: <soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:api="http://api.commons.panda.enjekt.org/">\r <soapenv:Header/>\r <soapenv:Body>\r <api:addPan>\r <!--Optional:-->\r <api:arg0>\r <!--Idempotent. Send Add of same PAN results in same token back:-->\r <pan>12345678901234567</pan>\r </api:arg0>\r </api:addPan>\r </soapenv:Body>\r </soapenv:Envelope>

con:call.name: Request PAN Back
con:call.con:request: <soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:api="http://api.commons.panda.enjekt.org/">\r <soapenv:Header/>\r <soapenv:Body>\r <api:getPan>\r <!--Optional:-->\r <api:arg0>\r <!--Replace this the token recieved from the Add PAN:-->\r <token>12345679845244567</token>\r </api:arg0>\r </api:getPan>\r </soapenv:Body>\r </soapenv:Envelope>
